{"tid":2368293,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"溝女王離婚冇對外公布","createTime":"2021-01-16T05:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-16T08:28:51.000Z","uid":123587,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"40c014bc9f6196b33e733d4342b0324a28a61c3f","tid":2368293,"uid":123587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:22:05.000Z","msg":"其實娛樂圈真係好多賤男，我 #哈比人 都識唔少。好似大台嘅「 #溝女王」，雖然一早結咗婚，但見一個溝一個，經常同女拍檔傳緋聞，當老婆冇到。講真「溝女王」嘅 #老婆 都係圈中人，對於老公偷食點會唔知呀，不過每次質問老公都吵大鑊，兩個關係愈嚟愈差。「溝女王」漸漸唔返屋企，索性搬竇瘟女，搞到老婆勁心淡，於是去搵師傅問前程，點知老婆愈講愈激動，喺師傅面前喊到收唔到聲，真係陰公豬，之後老婆決定離婚，不過為咗小朋友，先至冇對外公布，難為「溝女王」成日扮好老竇，真係世紀賤男！"},{"pid":"4b80025d4838966f7dc49ce2b6702dbf90923017","tid":2368293,"uid":339272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:31:19.000Z","msg":"姓咩的"},{"pid":"be6d1add0cb0fe4e635dc14dbb5345258666b52a","tid":2368293,"uid":238214,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:32:09.000Z","msg":"Signal Wong 啦.<br />\n係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9074ac8e556dfd7cf760e9bb11389eaa66aff5a","tid":2368293,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:32:29.000Z","msg":"Signal<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bd31c69c16a69c47c9c03e04a09f36a2732f62f","tid":2368293,"uid":337336,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"姓黃？黃咩信？"},{"pid":"75f50890b5cbdd5c201ca9fb1cdc29f495e455e4","tid":2368293,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:41:29.000Z","msg":"息怒皇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2cb614688a199361c054867c1a6b7a5bee9792","tid":2368293,"uid":32667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-16T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b78e709ead47d9bd6417539b9babab742b0dc7c1","tid":2368293,"uid":21716,"like":37,"dislik